Uploaded files help you install OpenCV on Ubuntu 12.04.
To install Opencv to your computer
#Login in as a root
sudo -i 
#Check for updates with command 
apt-get update 
#Install updates if any 
apt-get ugrade -y 
#Install git package 
apt-get install git -y 
#Clone installation script from github, use command   
git clone git://github.com/osoomuk/robosoomuk-.git 
#After that go to create directory robosoomuk
cd robosoomuk 
#Execute OpenCV installation script 
bash install.sh  
